Package primitives

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Coordinate
    Class Coordinate is the basic class representing a coordinate for Cartesian coordinate system.
    Point3D
    Point3D class represents point in 3D Cartesian coordinate system by three coordinates
    Ray
    Ray class represents a ray in 3D Cartesian coordinate system by point and vector
    Util
    Util class is used for some internal utilities, e.g. controlling accuracy
    Vector
    Vector class represents vector in 3D Cartesian coordinate system by Point3D
